[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- [ ] `examples/pipeline.yaml` has the `fix` phase and the new `bug` / `bug-complex` workflows[39m                                                             [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- [ ] Default config includes the `fix` phase[39m                                                                                                              [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- [ ] `cobuild init-skills` copies the new skill to a fresh repo correctly[39m                                                                                 [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- [ ] `cobuild explain` renders the new workflows without errors[39m                                                                                           [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- [ ] The existing `investigate` skill at `skills/investigate/bug-investigation.md` is untouched (Task I handles its header update)[39m                        [49m
[48;5;237m[38;5;231m- [ ] `go build ./...` and `go vet ./...` pass[39m                                                                                                             [49m
